data.description:
Waiting for it's new owner! Welcome to this lovely home that features both an Office+Den! The Den attaches to a bath & closet and could very easily be converted into a 4th bedroom to fit your needs! Making this home 4 beds+Office!

As you enter you are greeted by an open concept floor plan, with soaring ceilings & large windows that fill the space with natural light. The gourmet chef's kitchen boasts 2 fridges, an island, breakfast bar & huge pantry. Retreat to the primary suite, complete with a spa-like bathroom, 2 walk-in closets & a loft. The additional bedrooms are generously sized with walk-in closets and share a Jack & Jill bath. Enjoy the lovely Arizona weather in your private courtyard & backyard oasis with built-in BBQ! Easy access to I-17 & highway 51 make commuting a breeze! Additional features to note - there is two-car garage with tons of built-in storage, a large laundry room with sink & lots of cabinet space - there is no shortage of storage here! Freshly painted in June of '23, new tankless hot water heater installed in 2021, new HVAC units installed in 2020, and new owned-water softener loop installed in 2022. Low maintenance landscape with a full drip irrigation system!

Tucked away behind the private gates of Courtyards at Northern, on a coveted corner lot, this is the one! With its prime location you will have easy access to a wide array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. The nearby golf courses, hiking trails, & parks provide endless opportunities for outdoor recreation. Royal Palm Park is less than a 1/2 mile from the home and features numerous playgrounds. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours today!
